划文件\n- `research/reports/A股情绪规则二正式验证计划_20260327.md`\n\n这份计划已经明确了：\n- **冻结规则一**\n- **固定规则二两套候选**\n  - 主候选：`hot>=85 & score<=50 & S5 & reduce/block & 看空/强烈看空`\n  - 高置信候选：`hot>=90 & score<=40 & S5 & reduce/block & 看空/强烈看空`\n- **验证顺序**\n  - 先样本外验证\n  - 再交易层验证\n  - 最后影子运行\n\n### 2）样本外验证入口已确认\n已确认可复用脚本入口可用：\n- `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_stock_analysis_overlay_walkforward_validation.py`\n- `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_exit_rule_walkforward_validation.py`\n\n两条 `--help` 都已通过，说明首轮正式验证入口已经准备好，不是空口计划。\n\n### 3）ACTIVE_TASK 已真实收口\n- `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 当前状态：`done`\n\n## git 提交\n这轮我做了两次可核验提交：\n\n- `e4c5ffd` — `Add rule2 sentiment formal validation plan`\n- `b497e68` — `Close ACTIVE_TASK for rule2 validation planning`\n\n如果只看最新收口提交，用这个：\n- **`b497e68`**\n\n## 我接下来的动作\n我下一轮直接开始跑**规则二首轮样本外验证**，优先产出新的验证结果文件，不再重复问你确认。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a18d76e314b89270169c657c9eebc8198a3b76beff03cd101\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":65551,"output":1422,"cacheRead":22016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88989,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774606257978,"responseId":"resp_0a18d76e314b89270169c657b316a48198ab3c8b2aeae6e842"}}
