ow --path checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":20},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 scripts/active_task_cli.py show --path checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":20}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cDzy4BDiemLA2LdoghY3ONN4|fc_0a18d76e314b89270169c65daf932c8198a4cdadb63208563f","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/A股情绪规则二正式验证计划_20260327.md"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/A股情绪规则二正式验证计划_20260327.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5hkkGaLRiF9Enu5K2jzwCFvX|fc_0a18d76e314b89270169c65daf93348198b9908d79c23a1554","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_sentiment_threshold_scan.py","offset":1,"limit":260},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_sentiment_threshold_scan.py\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":260}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":96808,"output":1671,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98479,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774607750634,"responseId":"resp_0a18d76e314b89270169c65d87d0f08198b68ad15d19d90f54"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b6a268f4","parentId":"69eb3585","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:36:32.527Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ZF3gVLrpm6fPZ0rxRxzprBj8|fc_0a18d76e314b89270169c65daf931c81989fada4c6cbcfc47d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"path\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\",\n  \"status\": \"done\",\n  \"updated\": \"2026-03-27 18:12\",\n  \"current\": [],\n  \"next\": [],\n  \"completed_count\": 5,\n  \"evidence_count\": 7,\n  \"blockers\": []\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":263,"aggregated":"{\n  \"path\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\",\n  \"status\": \"done\",\n  \"updated\": \"2026-03-27 18:12\",\n  \"current\": [],\n  \"next\": [],\n  \"completed_count\": 5,\n  \"evidence_count\": 7,\n  \"blockers\": []\n}","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774607792516}}
{"type":"message","id":"158e81ac","parentId":"b6a268f4","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:36:32.536Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cDzy4BDiemLA2LdoghY3ONN4|fc_0a18d76e314b89270169c65daf932c8198a4cdadb63208563f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# A股情绪规则二正式验证计划（2026-03-27）\n\n生成时间：2026-03-27 18:09（Asia/Shanghai）\n\n## 一、当前已确认结论\n\n### 1. 规则一暂不继续主攻\n在当前 8 因子口径下，规则一（极冷修复放行）即使完成一轮阈值扫描，最优组合仍然劣于同日基线：\n\n- 最优扫描结果：`cold_prev<=20 & rebound_now>25 & score_min>=55`\n- 平均未来收益：`+0.1648%`\n- 同日基线平均收益：`+0.4497%`\n- 相对同日基线：`-0.2849%`\n\n结论：\n**规则一当前不进入正式门禁候选，只保留为研究项。**\n\n### 2. 规则二继续作为主线候选\n规则二（极热衰减拦截）在重新阈值扫描后重新恢复统计意义：\n\n- 严格高置信候选：`hot>=90 & score<=40`\n  - 样本数：`5`\n  - 避免损失优势：`+2.7843%`\n- 可执行主候选：`hot>=85 & score<=50`\n  - 样本数：`15`\n  - 避免损失优势：`+1.2196%`\n\n结论：\n**市场情绪因子不是“没用”，而是更适合用于高热衰减拦截，不适合继续硬撑极冷修复放行。**\n\n---\n\n## 二、正式验证对象\n\n### 候选 A：主执行候选\n- `hot >= 85`\n- `score <= 50`\n- `price_action_state_code == S5`\n- `ai_decision in {reduce, block}`\n- `trend_prediction in {看空, 强烈看空}`\n\n定位：\n- 样本量更可用\n- 适合先做样本外验证与影子运行\n\n### 候选 B：高置信候选\n- `hot >= 90`\n- `score <= 40`\n- `price_action_state_code == S5`\n- `ai_decision in {reduce, block}`\n- `trend_prediction in {看空, 强烈看空}`\n\n定位：\n- edge 更高\n- 样本更少\n- 更适合作为二级确认层，不单独直接上线\n\n---\n\n## 三、变量分工原则\n\n### 快变量：主触发\n- 成交量\n- 换手率\n- 涨停数\n- 北向代理\n- RSI\n\n### 慢变量：背景过滤\n- 两融余额\n- 股债收益差\n- 开放式基金仓位\n\n执行原则：\n**慢变量不直接决定“拦不拦”，而是决定“这个拦截信号是否需要更保守处理”。**\n\n---\n\n## 四、正式验证顺序\n\n### 第 1 步：样本外验证（优先）\n目标：确认候选 A / B 不是只在当前样本里好看。\n\n拟执行口径：\n1. 用现有明细 `research/reports/sentiment_gate_shadow_validation_detail_20260327_window_ext.csv`\n2. 先做固定训练 / 验证切分\n3. 再做滚动前推窗口验证\n4. 比较：\n   - 候选 A vs 候选 B\n   - 相对同日基线的避免损失优势\n   - 样本量稳定性\n   - 最差窗口表现\n\n验收重点：\n- 样本外仍保持正向避免损失优势\n- 不能只靠 1~2 个窗口撑结果\n- 最差窗口不能明显失控\n\n### 第 2 步：交易层验证\n目标：确认统计 edge 能否转成真实可执行收益改善。\n\n重点看：\n- 是否真正减少坏交易\n- 是否误杀强趋势样本\n- 加入手续费 / 滑点后是否仍值得保留\n\n### 第 3 步：影子运行\n目标：不上硬门禁，先连续旁路观察。\n\n执行方式：\n- 每天对候选 A / B 做影子打标\n- 记录“如果今天拦截，会影响哪些样本”\n- 连续观察一段时间后再决定是否进正式门禁\n\n---\n\n## 五、可直接复用的脚本入口\n\n当前仓内已确认存在的可复用验证脚本：\n\n### 1. overlay 样本外验证脚本\n- `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_stock_analysis_overlay_walkforward_validation.py`\n\n用途：\n- 训练 / 验证切分\n- 滚动前推窗口选择\n- 输出 JSON / Markdown / 多份 CSV\n\n### 2. walkforward 通用窗口脚本\n- `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_exit_rule_walkforward_validation.py`\n\n用途：\n- 提供 train/test/step 的滚动窗口能力\n- 可复用其窗口划分逻辑作为规则二样本外验证的骨架\n\n### 3. 当前已完成的规则二扫描脚本\n- `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_sentiment_threshold_scan.py`\n\n用途：\n- 保留为规则二阈值候选生成入口\n- 不再直接把扫描结果当最终上线依据，必须经过样本外验证\n\n---\n\n## 六、本轮建议动作\n\n### 立即执行\n1. 冻结规则一，不再继续主攻\n2. 固定规则二候选 A / B\n3. 启动首轮样本外验证准备\n\n### 暂不执行\n1. 不直接把规则二硬接入正式门禁\n2. 不继续无上限扩阈值网格，避免过拟合\n3. 不把慢变量升格为主触发\n\n---\n\n## 七、验收口径\n\n只有同时满足下面条件，规则二才可以进入正式门禁候选：\n\n1. 样本外验证为正\n2. 滚动窗口多数跑赢同日基线\n3. 最差窗口不过度失真\n4. 影子运行期间未出现明显误杀强趋势问题\n\n若以上任一不满足：\n**继续保留在研究候选层，不进入正式门禁。**\n\n---\n\n## 一句话结论\n\n**当前最优策略不是继续争论“情绪因子有没有用”，而是冻结规则一、收敛规则二，并用样本外验证 + 影子运行决定它能否正式上岗。**\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774607792526}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2a69304","parentId":"158e81ac","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:36:32.547Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5hkkGaLRiF9Enu5K2jzwCFvX|fc_0a18d76e314b89270169c65daf93348198b9908d79c23a1554","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nimport json\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nWORKSPACE = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace')\nREPORT_DIR = WORKSPACE / 'research' / 'reports'\nDEFAULT_DETAIL = REPORT_DIR / 'sentiment_gate_shadow_validation_detail_20260327_window_ext.csv'\nDEFAULT_PANEL = REPORT_DIR / 'docx14_sentiment_factor_panel_20260327_window_ext.csv'\n\nFAST_Z_COLS = [\n    'ashare_trading_volume_z60',\n    'ashare_turnover_rate_z60',\n    'limit_up_stock_count_z60',\n    'northbound_trading_total_z60',\n    'rsi_index_z60',\n]\nSLOW_Z_COLS = [\n    'margin_balance_z60',\n    'equity_bond_yield_spread_z60',\n    'open_fund_stock_position_ratio_z60',\n]\n\n\ndef rolling_percentile(series: pd.Series, window: int = 60) -> pd.Series:\n    values = pd.to_numeric(series, errors='coerce')\n    out: list[float | None] = []\n    for idx in range(len(values)):\n        start = max(0, idx - window + 1)\n        hist = values.iloc[start : idx + 1].dropna()\n        cur = values.iloc[idx]\n        if hist.empty or pd.isna(cur):\n            out.append(None)\n            continue\n        out.append(round(float((hist <= cur).mean() * 100.0), 4))\n    return pd.Series(out, index=series.index, dtype='float64')\n\n\ndef bool_series(series: pd.Series) -> pd.Series:\n    return series.astype('boolean').fillna(False)\n\n\ndef summarize(frame: pd.DataFrame) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    completed = frame.dropna(subset=['future_return_pct']).copy()\n    count = int(len(frame))\n    completed_count = int(len(completed))\n    avg_ret = round(float(completed['future_return_pct'].mean()), 4) if completed_count else None\n    med_ret = round(float(completed['future_return_pct'].median()), 4) if completed_count else None\n    win_rate = round(float((completed['future_return_pct'] > 0).mean() * 100.0), 2) if completed_count else None\n    return {\n        'count': count,\n        'completed_count': completed_count,\n        'avg_future_return_pct': avg_ret,\n        'median_future_return_pct': med_ret,\n        'win_rate_pct': win_rate,\n    }\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    ap = argparse.ArgumentParser(description='8因子情绪阈值扫描 + 快慢变量拆层验证')\n    ap.add_argument('--detail-csv', default=str(DEFAULT_DETAIL))\n    ap.add_argument('--panel-csv', default=str(DEFAULT_PANEL))\n    ap.add_argument('--date-tag', default=datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d'))\n    args = ap.parse_args()\n\n    detail = pd.read_csv(Path(args.detail_csv).expanduser().resolve())\n    panel = pd.read_csv(Path(args.panel_csv).expanduser().resolve())\n    detail.columns = [str(c).lstrip('\\ufeff') for c in detail.columns]\n    panel.columns = [str(c).lstrip('\\ufeff') for c in panel.columns]\n\n    detail['date_key'] = pd.to_numeric(detail['date_key'], errors='coerce').fillna(0).astype(int)\n    detail['future_return_pct'] = pd.to_numeric(detail['future_return_pct'], errors='coerce')\n    detail['sentiment_score'] = pd.to_numeric(detail['sentiment_score'], errors='coerce')\n    detail['proxy_sentiment_percentile_60d'] = pd.to_numeric(detail['proxy_sentiment_percentile_60d'], errors='coerce')\n    detail['proxy_prev_sentiment_percentile_60d'] = pd.to_numeric(detail['proxy_prev_sentiment_percentile_60d'], errors='coerce')\n    detail['risk_approved'] = detail['risk_approved'].astype(str).str.lower().eq('true')\n    detail['trend_exhaustion_flag'] = bool_series(detail['trend_exhaustion_flag'])\n    detail['failed_breakout_flag'] = bool_series(detail['failed_breakout_flag'])\n    detail['state_weakening'] = detail['trend_exhaustion_flag'] | detail['failed_breakout_flag'] | detail['price_action_state_code'].astype(str).eq('S5')\n    detail['ai_decision_norm'] = detail['ai_decision'].astype(str).str.lower().str.strip()\n    detail['trend_prediction_norm'] = detail['trend_prediction'].astype(str).str.strip()\n\n    panel['trade_date'] = pd.to_numeric(panel['trade_date'], errors='coerce').fillna(0).astype(int)\n    panel = panel.sort_values('trade_date').reset_index(drop=True)\n    panel['fast_raw_score'] = panel[FAST_Z_COLS].apply(pd.to_numeric, errors='coerce').mean(axis=1, skipna=True)\n    panel['slow_raw_score'] = panel[SLOW_Z_COLS].apply(pd.to_numeric, errors='coerce').mean(axis=1, skipna=True)\n    panel['fast_pct_60'] = rolling_percentile(panel['fast_raw_score'], 60)\n    panel['slow_pct_60'] = rolling_percentile(panel['slow_raw_score'], 60)\n    panel['fast_prev_pct_60'] = panel['fast_pct_60'].shift(1)\n    panel['slow_prev_pct_60'] = panel['slow_pct_60'].shift(1)\n    panel['fast_gt_slow'] = panel['fast_pct_60'] > panel['slow_pct_60']\n    panel['slow_supportive'] = panel['slow_pct_60'] >= 50.0\n    panel['slow_hot'] = panel['slow_pct_60'] >= 60.0\n\n    detail = detail.merge(\n        panel[['trade_date', 'fast_pct_60', 'slow_pct_60', 'fast_prev_pct_60', 'slow_prev_pct_60', 'fast_gt_slow', 'slow_supportive', 'slow_hot']],\n        left_on='date_key',\n        right_on='trade_date',\n        how='left',\n    )\n    if 'trade_date_y' in detail.columns:\n        detail = detail.drop(columns=['trade_date_y'])\n\n    baseline = detail[detail['risk_approved']].copy()\n\n    rule1_rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    for cold_prev in [5, 10, 15, 20]:\n        for rebound_now in [10, 15, 20, 25]:\n            if rebound_now <= cold_prev:\n                continue\n            for score_min in [45, 50, 55, 60]:\n                mask = (\n                    detail['risk_approved']\n                    & (detail['proxy_prev_sentiment_percentile_60d'] <= cold_prev)\n                    & (detail['proxy_sentiment_percentile_60d'] > rebound_now)\n                    & detail['ai_decision_norm'].ne('block')\n                    & detail['trend_prediction_norm'].isin(['看多', '强烈看多'])\n                    & (~detail['state_weakening'])\n                    & (detail['sentiment_score'] >= score_min)\n                )\n                sample = detail[mask].copy()\n                days = sorted(sample['date_key'].dropna().unique().tolist())\n                same_day = baseline[baseline['date_key'].isin(days)].copy() if days else baseline.iloc[0:0].copy()\n                s = summarize(sample)\n                b = summarize(same_day)\n                edge = None\n                if s['avg_future_return_pct'] is not None and b['avg_future_return_pct'] is not None:\n                    edge = round(s['avg_future_return_pct'] - b['avg_future_return_pct'], 4)\n                rule1_rows.append({\n                    'cold_prev': cold_prev,\n                    'rebound_now': rebound_now,\n                    'score_min': score_min,\n                    'count': s['count'],\n                    'avg_future_return_pct': s['avg_future_return_pct'],\n                    'win_rate_pct': s['win_rate_pct'],\n                    'same_day_avg_future_return_pct': b['avg_future_return_pct'],\n                    'edge_vs_same_day_baseline_pct': edge,\n                })\n    rule1_df = pd.DataFrame(rule1_rows).sort_values(['edge_vs_same_day_baseline_pct', 'count'], ascending=[False, False]).reset_index(drop=True)\n\n    rule2_rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    for hot_cut in [80, 85, 90, 95]:\n        for score_max in [40, 45, 50, 55]:\n            mask = (\n                detail['risk_approved']\n                & (detail['proxy_sentiment_percentile_60d'] >= hot_cut)\n                & detail['state_weakening']\n                & detail['ai_decision_norm'].isin(['reduce', 'block'])\n                & detail['trend_prediction_norm'].isin(['看空', '强烈看空'])\n                & (detail['sentiment_score'] <= score_max)\n            )\n            sample = detail[mask].copy()\n            days = sorted(sample['date_key'].dropna().unique().tolist())\n            same_day = baseline[baseline['date_key'].isin(days)].copy() if days else baseline.iloc[0:0].copy()\n            s = summarize(sample)\n            b = summarize(same_day)\n            avoid_edge = None\n            if s['avg_future_return_pct'] is not None and b['avg_future_return_pct'] is not None:\n                avoid_edge = round(b['avg_future_return_pct'] - s['avg_future_return_pct'], 4)\n            rule2_rows.append({\n                'hot_cut': hot_cut,\n                'score_max': score_max,\n                'count': s['count'],\n                'avg_future_return_pct': s['avg_future_return_pct'],\n                'win_rate_pct': s['win_rate_pct'],\n                'same_day_avg_future_return_pct': b['avg_future_return_pct'],\n                'avoid_loss_edge_vs_same_day_baseline_pct': avoid_edge,\n            })\n    rule2_df = pd.DataFrame(rule2_rows).sort_values(['avoid_loss_edge_vs_same_day_baseline_pct', 'count'], ascending=[False, False]).reset_index(drop=True)\n\n    layer_rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    layer_defs = {\n        'rule1_fast_only': (\n            detail['risk_approved']\n            & (detail['fast_prev_pct_60'] <= 10)\n            & (detail['fast_pct_60'] > 15)\n            & detail['ai_decision_norm'].ne('block')\n            & detail['trend_prediction_norm'].isin(['看多', '强烈看多'])\n            & (~detail['state_weakening'])\n        ),\n        'rule1_fast_plus_slow_supportive': (\n            detail['risk_approved']\n            & (detail['fast_prev_pct_60'] <= 10)\n            & (detail['fast_pct_60'] > 15)\n            & detail['ai_decision_norm'].ne('block')\n            & detail['trend_prediction_norm'].isin(['看多', '强烈看多'])\n            & (~detail['state_weakening'])\n            & bool_series(detail['slow_supportive'])\n        ),\n        'rule2_fast_hot_decay': (\n            detail['risk_approved']\n            & (detail['fast_pct_60'] >= 90)\n            & detail['state_weakening']\n            & detail['ai_decision_norm'].isin(['reduce', 'block'])\n            & detail['trend_prediction_norm'].isin(['看空', '强烈看空'])\n        ),\n        'rule2_fast_hot_plus_slow_hot': (\n            detail['risk_approved']\n            & (detail['fast_pct_60'] >= 90)\n            & detail['state_weakening']\n            & detail['ai_decision_norm'].isin(['reduce', 'block'])\n            & detail['trend_prediction_norm'].isin(['看空', '强烈看空'])\n            & bool_series(detail['slow_hot'])\n        ),\n    }\n    for name, mask in layer_defs.items():\n        sample = detail[mask].copy()\n        days = sorted(sample['date_key'].dropna().unique().tolist())\n        same_day = baseline[baseline['date_key'].isin(days)].copy() if days else baseline.iloc[0:0].copy()\n        s = summarize(sample)\n        b = summarize(same_day)\n        edge = None\n        if s['avg_future_return_pct'] is not None and b['avg_future_return_pct'] is not None:\n            edge = round(s['avg_future_return_pct'] - b['avg_future_return_pct'], 4)\n        layer_rows.append({\n            'variant': name,\n            'count': s['count'],\n            'avg_future_return_pct': s['avg_future_return_pct'],\n            'win_rate_pct': s['win_rate_pct'],\n            'same_day_avg_future_return_pct': b['avg_future_return_pct'],\n            'edge_vs_same_day_baseline_pct': edge,\n        })\n    layer_df = pd.DataFrame(layer_rows)\n\n    payload = {\n        'generated_at': datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'),\n        'detail_csv': str(Path(args.detail_csv).expanduser().resolve()),\n        'panel_csv': str(Path(args.panel_csv).expanduser().resolve()),\n        'rule1_top10': rule1_df.head(10).to_dict(orient='records'),\n        'rule2_top10': rule2_df.head(10).to_dict(orient='records'),\n        'layer_validation': layer_df.to_dict(orient='records'),\n    }\n\n    out_json = REPORT_DIR / f'sentiment_threshold_scan_{args.date_tag}.json'\n    out_md = REPORT_DIR / f'sentiment_threshold_scan_{args.date_tag}.md'\n    out_rule1 = REPORT_DIR / f'sentiment_threshold_scan_rule1_{args.date_tag}.csv'\n    out_rule2 = REPORT_DIR / f'sentiment_threshold_scan_rule2_{args.date_tag}.csv'\n    out_layer = REPORT_DIR / f'sentiment_layer_validation_{args.date_tag}.csv'\n\n    rule1_df.to_csv(out_rule1, index=False, encoding='utf-8-sig')\n    rule2_df.to_csv(out_rule2, index=False, encoding='utf-8-sig')\n    layer_df.to_csv(out_layer, index=False, encoding='utf-8-sig')\n    out_json.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding='utf-8')\n\n    md = [\n        '# 8因子情绪阈值扫描与快慢变量拆层验证',\n        '',\n        f\"- 生成时间：{payload['generated_at']}\",\n        f\"- 明细：`{payload['detail_csv']}`\",\n        f\"- 面板：`{payload['panel_csv']}`\",\n        '',\n        '## 规则一阈值扫描 Top 10',\n    ]\n    for row in payload['rule1_top10']:\n\n[21 more lines in file. Use offset=261 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774607792536}}
{"type":"message","id":"2723f788","parentId":"f2a69304","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:37:08.458Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Preparing data processing**\n\nI need to run on the current detail CSV and check if the existing candidate fields are sufficient. It seems like using proxy_sentiment_percentile_60d could work since that’s what the scan script used. But the plan mentions needing hot candidates at 85 or higher, which might be fast. The prior finetune report indicates we should have fast_pct_60 at 85, but it’s not in the detail CSV. I can derive it by joining the panel and computing fast_pct_60 from the appropriate columns like the scan script does. I’m thinking the new script should use the panel CSV to join and incorporate fast_pct_60, and it might be good to focus on only the S5 state as well.\n\n**Computing training splits**\n\nI think I need to compute on the training split with rolling windows. First, I should build a sorted list of unique trade dates. Then, I’ll create a holdout split, using 70/30 with a minimum of 42 test days. For each candidate, I want to compute the sample count, mean return, and the same-day baseline mean, while avoiding the edge calculated as baseline minus sample. I’ll choose a preferred candidate based on avoiding edges, and evaluate it on validation. I also want to build rolling windows with 168 for training and 42 for testing, stepping by 21. For each window, I’ll choose a candidate based on avoiding edges and minimum counts. If the count is 0 or edge is None, that could be a flag to set it as bad. Then I’ll evaluate on the test set. Finally, I'll summarize the metrics for candidates A and B, deciding based on positive test edges and ensuring a robust profile mean.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0a18d76e314b89270169c65db40c9481989876773075267962\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpxl3DZdDOCAgI8RyGFN-xK2wHRcqEt4PSqPBc6st32xdCsXYRHdufRU0_L46WpjKM8S1xOaLvA7DyK1x4lQ