and future_return_pct. I’ll create a simple script that reads the same detail and panel, computes fast_pct60, and generates rows for both the main and reference candidates. Using the same-day baseline average sounds good too!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"先说实话：**从上次 18:56 收口到你刚才这条消息之间，没有新增产物。**  \n我刚核对了最新提交，停在：\n\n- `c1d26ce` — `Close ACTIVE_TASK for candidate A local scan`\n- `9f265f5` — `Add candidate A local scan and shadow plan`\n\n我不拿“计划中”冒充进度。现在我直接把下一步真正落下：**把规则二影子运行做成可落盘的台账脚本，并产出第一份回填台账。**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a18d76e314b89270169c6726d10a48198877ed783c2e148cf\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ELJba4iC7rH53LY8quwpq2Z6|fc_0a18d76e314b89270169c6727bfd588198b324ebad6a9a5d41","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md","content":"Status: active\nPriority: P1\nStarted: 2026-03-27 20:07\nUpdated: 2026-03-27 20:07\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 推进得如何了\nResume Entry: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/A股情绪规则二影子运行方案_20260327.md\n\n## Goal\n- 将规则二主影子候选（85/50）与参考候选（87/55）落成可回填、可持续记录的影子台账执行链，并生成首份历史回填验收件。\n\n## Acceptance\n- 落地一份规则二影子台账脚本或等效自动化入口\n- 至少生成一份历史回填影子台账（CSV/JSON/Markdown 任两种以上）\n- 提交本轮产物到 git，并给出可核验提交 hash\n\n## Current\n- 落地规则二影子台账脚本并定义主候选/参考候选字段口径\n\n## Next\n- 运行历史回填，生成首份影子台账与摘要报告\n- 更新 ACTIVE_TASK 状态并提交 git\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-03-27 18:56] 已完成候选 A 局部稳健性扫描与影子运行方案\n\n## Evidence\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/A股情绪规则二影子运行方案_20260327.md\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/A股情绪验证链第九轮_候选A局部稳健性扫描_20260327_candidateA_local.md\n- 主影子候选：`hot>=85 & score<=50 & S5 & reduce/block & 看空/强烈看空`\n- 参考候选：`hot>=87 & score<=55 & S5 & reduce/block & 看空/强烈看空`\n\n## Blockers\n- None\n\n## Rules\n- `Current` must contain exactly one active item.\n- After finishing `Current`, move it to `Completed`, add proof under `Evidence`, then promote the first item in `Next` into `Current`.\n- Prefer rebuilding the whole file once when switching to a new continuation phase, then use `active_task_cli.py advance` for later state changes.\n- After each write/update, verify the file with `python3 scripts/active_task_cli.py show --path checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md` before reporting the state.\n- Only set `Status: blocked` when the blocker is real and specific.\n- Only set `Status: done` when `Acceptance` is met.\n"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\",\"content\":\"Status: active\\nPriority: P1\\nStarted: 2026-03-27 20:07\\nUpdated: 2026-03-27 20:07\\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\\nOwner: main-session\\nUser Trigger: 推进得如何了\\nResume Entry: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/A股情绪规则二影子运行方案_20260327.md\\n\\n## Goal\\n- 将规则二主影子候选（85/50）与参考候选（87/55）落成可回填、可持续记录的影子台账执行链，并生成首份历史回填验收件。\\n\\n## Acceptance\\n- 落地一份规则二影子台账脚本或等效自动化入口\\n- 至少生成一份历史回填影子台账（CSV/JSON/Markdown 任两种以上）\\n- 提交本轮产物到 git，并给出可核验提交 hash\\n\\n## Current\\n- 落地规则二影子台账脚本并定义主候选/参考候选字段口径\\n\\n## Next\\n- 运行历史回填，生成首份影子台账与摘要报告\\n- 更新 ACTIVE_TASK 状态并提交 git\\n\\n## Completed\\n- [2026-03-27 18:56] 已完成候选 A 局部稳健性扫描与影子运行方案\\n\\n## Evidence\\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/A股情绪规则二影子运行方案_20260327.md\\n- /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/A股情绪验证链第九轮_候选A局部稳健性扫描_20260327_candidateA_local.md\\n- 主影子候选：`hot>=85 & score<=50 & S5 & reduce/block & 看空/强烈看空`\\n- 参考候选：`hot>=87 & score<=55 & S5 & reduce/block & 看空/强烈看空`\\n\\n## Blockers\\n- None\\n\\n## Rules\\n- `Current` must contain exactly one active item.\\n- After finishing `Current`, move it to `Completed`, add proof under `Evidence`, then promote the first item in `Next` into `Current`.\\n- Prefer rebuilding the whole file once when switching to a new continuation phase, then use `active_task_cli.py advance` for later state changes.\\n- After each write/update, verify the file with `python3 scripts/active_task_cli.py show --path checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md` before reporting the state.\\n- Only set `Status: blocked` when the blocker is real and specific.\\n- Only set `Status: done` when `Acceptance` is met.\\n\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_IEB2P2c3WqV0oYtMcD46LaWU|fc_0a18d76e314b89270169c6727bfd688198957cebed6219c6bd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 scripts/active_task_cli.py show --path checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":20},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 scripts/active_task_cli.py show --path checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":20}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":88543,"output":1881,"cacheRead":29184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119608,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774613077786,"responseId":"resp_0a18d76e314b89270169c67257ced4819890b3c9bbbf62b4b8"}}
