{"type":"message","id":"e2677849","parentId":"e718694d","timestamp":"2026-03-27T12:15:48.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Evaluating script improvements**\n\nI need to run the script to see if it works, but hopefully, no code changes are necessary. However, I should generate a report to confirm everything's functioning properly. A critical improvement would be to ensure the script checks for market breadth mismatches in event_watch since it currently doesn't compare the breadth to runtime, which totally makes sense.\n\nAdditionally, I should confirm that the source in event_watch matches the runtime risk state. Including checks on the latest JSON sync would be smart too.\n\n**Inspecting runtime and event watch**\n\nI need to take a peek at the current runtime and the event watch JSON to understand the fields better. It seems important to read the latest runtime data and check the current consistency output, though it looks like it might be nonexistent. I should also look into the latest details from event watch to gather more context. This inspection will help clarify things as I move forward.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0a18d76e314b89270169c674dff73481988cca1ccf619ca259\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpxnTsJmTZbO1FA6gkFPIWwKrCAKWcCuIXlmyBEjCXGnPBYD5zrFAwZPCyuIhGN2zF_7AlJWvx9ULIQrjQRy5ptk-48eTV4lctcgngsbEVIKW8Uf_BCqf3a5NgFMtMle59PjqKUWqDHGe8YFF2K0e-9b8nE2XTsefuJxKrC-4Kjk-xn6ghW5csnL0er3ZIMn6HFyd_hDeW5MyrPoy6Wzo1KyjwQnzZlcDAdNVY-EmDW-1_9lf0Ef68FIrEcSEI-XWFa9g9cV9IU-FR7FIK-b4LqqQff8tMwhcXGkQZepScJBJU6c1vllGEW1FTueLymTHxnFJPWfhC8lfgAz15nc8MaBZDXRxKkufBh7B69gNtrzy_LxOSo-WMduwPpP0PYJjOwEqwU-cSh7brkPfcqd2euGkAGm3U_1JsFmteKe41xWHz9VHDaKMqRNz2hXFUwzFmGbryJh_irS1GDIoaqOzYcFVnmtn5L3MLT48NjvDPohM79Sokz1AnhEPqr-13UT-n5W6_6i-XU4uXxwFk-_SKRwIXqKEDSCarioE5AZl8opRQPj_sbJLT3alZjLUNcLwlNWUdeFxxBpvMVoadUWWi7TCGWtwInkyZ5KKKe2GmHnNmt7hhYR9uYcHlTgSLZQ8OIenULaPek0kSGOjXdd7-EBRbg77zxVOOSW-ofYJO3aKY6kaxQYKfVqIghoM