c1N0_e-L7J1DwJsEmkGwyp7SHGm_hTa9In4DMpFCp4r\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 收到，已继续执行完 **P1-001 一致性收口**。\n\n## 当前阶段\n**P1-001 已完成正式收口验收。**\n\n## 本轮最小验收件\n### 1）补强脚本\n- `scripts/ensure_p1_001_consistency.py`\n\n本轮新增了两条关键收口逻辑：\n- **`event_watch.market_breadth` 与 runtime 强制对齐检查**\n- **dated → latest 强制同步**\n  - strategy report 同步\n  - event_watch 同步\n\n### 2）一致性刷新产物\n- `research/reports/p1_001_consistency_refresh_latest.json`\n- `research/reports/p1_001_consistency_refresh_latest.md`\n\n### 3）正式验收报告\n- `research/reports/P1_001一致性收口验收_20260327.md`\n\n## 关键结果\n### runtime / report / event_watch 当前已对齐\n当前关键字段统一为：\n\n- `mode = halt`\n- `halt_new_buy = true`\n- `market_breadth = 0.16370533040527052`\n\n其中：\n- strategy report 已刷新到新口径\n- `investment_research_event_watch_latest.json` 之前缺失，**这轮已由 dated 真源强制补齐**\n- event_watch 当前 source 为：\n  - `runtime_risk_state_latest`\n\n### 自动检验结果\n本轮补跑结果：\n\n- `python3 scripts/run_quant_p0_audit.py`\n  - `PASS`\n  - `finding_count = 0`\n\n- `python3 scripts/run_tester_scheduled_guard.py`\n  - `PASS`\n  - `issue_count = 0`\n\n## 这轮修到的真实问题\n不是空泛“复核”——这轮实际补掉的是：\n\n1. **event_watch 一致性检查之前没把 breadth 纳入**\n2. **根目录 event_watch latest 别名缺失**\n3. **strategy report 在 runtime 变化后可能滞后**\n\n现在这三点都已经纳入自动收口链。\n\n## git 提交\n这轮可核验提交：\n\n- `65fb857` — `Close P1-001 consistency gap`\n- `44f412f` — `Close ACTIVE_TASK for P1-001 consistency`\n\n如果只看最新收口提交：\n- **`44f412f`**\n\n## ACTIVE_TASK 状态\n- `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 当前状态：**`done`**\n\n一句话结论：\n\n**P1-001 这一项已经收口：runtime 成为唯一真源，report / event_watch 已统一到 mode、halt、breadth 和 latest 同步规则。**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a18d76e314b89270169c675d6c11c81989e02110c03d7c9b3\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":228,"output":740,"cacheRead":129792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130760,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":17746139634