{"type":"message","id":"61f84e30","parentId":"37ae0d33","timestamp":"2026-03-27T13:40:57.708Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Determining observation period**\n\nI need to consider how long the user should observe. I think mentioning a baseline of at least 20 trading days, or about 20 effective triggers, would be good. Ideally, it might take around 4-6 weeks, which translates to roughly a month. Since the user asked in plain language, I'll keep it concise. Perhaps I should explain that since we're not in execution yet, an extended observation period isn't necessary. I'll craft a clear response.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0a18d76e314b89270169c688e11ba481989562485fab54b204\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpxojlvXZOoKR4pE962qbiGxkQM-gH-PThnEmA8I5wjccqy6jHmPizOmfkDnAdhUH3YtiGPdhslPo25fVCry_TZ_7LxlIjfBWwnro9MUU9jvcUthQRl4MCmOww6DZeV2bACWIMwqy4YFCjjCivs0wiGdPFIvtLJrJUcdBcgWBKEzV1dcqaJsWdJt4Fo9Fhxp_h67rs8VhcRBFO3q-2Byz98VvMiC3dEXwQ4QlOG3kloNgCQV59I_F8LxO6rjl092agUrsE8JiYsdpPx6BUDvevOtjBw26P8Hr-ZszyVTG-ezWKHDLMeRSTnxv5vmW5laF2qQACYbI4tJxIKSWJrqGpXYgj4jZa-9Cm1nxGPnGVMD04N5o9dHpBFVbnC5shFZj71BNtYfkQXlh0tv-OTM_YAGfKCcoqchChtqPmK8S6QNaUXciIMF3MRsv5cdD4Ie23aBRjsOBeUUlEmodgSiNbyZxzhXjmHk5nraYwsDLASzujFQ9weOLXGEKEHJ7sqHXwpXIrc7vaTzJxI-dEq8D7vfXs5HhhdPx_8Uor8Vu9rC6a18tDqIWPb2FIXpfDMouZsDX1W-CZicw7JB3fJz40OzyfZF1PkahCXcgNrcKjAajQ9WpmE-f8Vcq-W4iOLND5rs4Ae_jILGZBQvHvRkZd520B0kCWgZioH3fPk6efZHEVTnjdCndrzGJn-x1d44XgSxBo9LZL47_96zWCDRXZpHe_Xk2KCcrQHE-ySwchJLDaFQTu8qOlig_TS8yEXNAVnprY4oPaW2ciDSKmPN1IfMRC335p6sIc1GVVaDd_hPsLlag6FK6RZH4Isn19e93pXImV2EeWxRBSdPsqQd_QuMfIGEgNJ3YXKAY8XsC6tD0MezZYjLFxoI7kdapxZb_qG1p8YPt08z5opSzczNIXRqUgob3ws-RLtqj5PRssXWrZn8oNDAmURpwmR4fx53Guc8CWxrbUzMZbOw5uLmeJ_c0m35Atfr0bvIVl_SfKolZBTWFWSMQfYhfAEltnAR0jGcRsHPh4meC0qe7UwG8jkLzd7cIXUXCPH6Ty20iG80_DR06RJKvfCIYsfrKb-eWbheJjeXpEcgq6q5JUrzwLcJLIi8S8NiXvfDcxKJ82ePc-zYC314sMFEZD-YbC8Ub1Xhm4A8a71Iie8HNU3JBfr9gft3GmBgPL5q6UWtHhsPpITHOPW4Fs5A96DFSlD6ZS3GOEQGB2n93b11DzuA-m_Y_5_eTbBu0RymBDQcNu-drTaLYEcst4cKXCbKaMbXs2cIklazOieITaFJamn_5l-tpB2KjzDC5v9_obM2N5_y5Bn8inRau5tY93pGDytsyIMGf2RZZGbY9DLHIu8WNkBN_zcg==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Determining observation period**\\n\\nI need to consider how long the user should observe. I think mentioning a baseline of at least 20 trading days, or about 20 effective triggers, would be good. Ideally, it might take around 4-6 weeks, which translates to roughly a month. Since the user asked in plain language, I'll keep it concise. Perhaps I should explain that since we're not in execution yet, an extended observation period isn't necessary. I'll craft a clear response.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 收到。**最低观察期我建议这样定：**\n\n## 先定一个“够用”的门槛\n**满足下面任一条，就做第一次正式复核：**\n\n- **20 个交易日**\n- **20 次有效触发**\n\n谁先到，就先复核。\n\n---\n\n## 说人话\n### 为什么不是 3 天、5 天就下结论？\n因为这套规则二现在最大的问题不是“完全没信号”，而是：\n\n- 样本还不够多\n- 有时候有效，有时候会翻\n- 太早下结论，容易被几笔样本骗到\n\n所以必须给它一点时间，看看它在**不同市场日子**里是不是都站得住。\n\n---\n\n## 我建议的节奏\n### 第一阶段：短观察\n- **先看 20 个交易日 / 20 次有效触发**\n- 这是“够不够继续留”的门槛\n\n### 第二阶段：再确认\n如果第一阶段结果还可以，再继续看到：\n- **40 个交易日**\n  或\n- **40 次有效触发**\n\n到这时候，基本就能判断：\n- 只是运气好一下\n- 还是真的有稳定价值\n\n---\n\n## 所以现在怎么定最合适？\n**最小观察期：20 个交易日 / 20 次有效触发**\n这是我建议的正式第一道门槛。\n\n一句话：\n\n**先观察到“20天或20次触发”，再决定要不要把它从影子观察往前推。**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a18d76e314b89270169c688e5e6f88198a846400e1977444a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":3299,"output":443,"cacheRead":81024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84766,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774618845761,"responseId":"resp_0a18d76e314b89270169c688dfdccc81988910072c87e4a899"}}
